messages.message:
Hey team, I wonder if there's a recent change to this file that made `repo/picker_utils` not available in local env when `"enable_aihub_public": true,` is set?
https://github.com/instabase/instabase/blob/master/webserver/server-nginx/config/nginx-config-template.jinja.yml
For me, the nodes in the file picker is not loading properly in my local env until I added `repo/picker_utils` there. But I remembered that we've already added this in for aihub a month ago.
i put up a PR for the fix https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/44225
